title: The Avengers (De Wrekers) - 1967 Episodes 4-6 (DVDR)
description:
The Avengers was an English television series featuring secret agents in 1960s Britain. The programmes were made by TV company Associated British Corporation, and created by its Head of Drama Sydney Newman. It was an early example of the spy-fi genre, combining secret agent storylines with science fiction elements. 

This classic series follows the adventures of John Steed and Emma Peel, two secret agents whose mission is to face the most mysterious and dangerous situations. 


Season 5 (1967): 

Episode 4: Thee See Through Man 
Episode 5: The Bird Who Knew Too Much 
Episode 6: The Winged Avenger
